name: Ptazeta
description: Ptazeta is a trap singer from the Canary Islands whose fame has grown like crazy in just a few months. She started uploading her own songs to Instagram to soon become one of the sensations of the urban scene. With little more than twenty years old, she accumulates millions of reproductions on YouTube and other digital platforms of her songs and video clips.

name: Bad Gyal
description: arelo was born in Vilassar de Mar, Spain, the eldest of five children,[8] daughter of the actor and dubbing actor Eduard Farelo.[9][10] He worked for international productions such as The Lord of the Rings and Star Wars. After taking selectividad, Farelo studied a degree in fashion design at the University of Barcelona. While attending university and working at a call centre, she released Pai in April 2016, an adaptation of work by Rihanna, adapting the lyrics to a mixture of Spanish, Catalan and English.
